    "description": {
      "description": "<p><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\">Se autoflagela fazendo um pouco de sangue jorrar, para curar ou ferir a contraparte do tratado de sangue.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Esforço:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 2.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo:</span> 1 ação.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dificuldade:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 13.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> [ESP+MS] Biológico: Vital.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> recebo o Dano, e cura o dobro desse Dano em PV ou causa o dobro em Dano Existencial a contraparte do <em>tratado de sangue</em>. Cada </span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family:'MS Mincho';mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">Ⓐ</span><span lang=\"JA\"> </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast-font-family:'MS Gothic';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">reduz o dano causado a si em 25%.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Pré-requisitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> <em>Tratado de sangue.</em></span></p>",
